description: The best BBQ east of Texas is right around the corner, thanks to Pittsburgh Smokehouse! Cooked low and slow for that perfect BBQ flavor and tenderness, these are real stick-to-your-ribs meals made to satisfy your hunger unlike anything else around. If you're hungry for delicious brisket, pulled pork, ribs, and more, there's nobody better than Pittsburgh Smokehouse!
name: Pittsburgh Smokehouse
